						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Pallava Aparājita = c. 900 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Tamil verse. Records that a certain Nambi-Appi built the temple at Tiruttaṉiyal with granite. The verse <hi rend="italic">(venba)</hi> is said to have been composed by Perumānaḍikaḷ. This Nambi Appi figures in another inscription <hi rend="italic">(AR. 435 of 1905).</hi></p>						

						<p>(Published in <hi rend="italic">SII</hi> Vol. XII, No. 94.)</p>						

